       `display:none` (collapsed/inactive cards), so this doesn't touch that state. */
    min-height: 13.87rem; /* 221.94px — target combined footprint (277.91px, O2's own title+body) minus O1/O3/O4's shared 55.97px single-line title height */
  }
  /* O2's title is uniquely 2 lines (`.card-title--split`, ~110px vs the other three's
