     above (which would otherwise over-inflate it past the target). */
  .card--o2 .card-body {
    min-height: 10.5rem; /* 168px — O2's own natural body height; combined with its own ~110px title this already hits the same target the other three reach via the larger shared min-height */
  }

  .card-footer {
    margin-top: auto; /* pins the divider+chips flush to the card's own bottom regardless of how much (or how little — O2/O3/O4 have no body) content precedes it, reproducing the design's fixed chip-row position at every card's own bottom. Kept as-is for the COLLAPSED state (card-body/subtitle are display:none there, so this is the only thing positioning the footer) — only overridden for the active state below. */
    border-top: 0.125rem solid var(--color-ink-alt);
